wikipedia_page.main: William Clere Leonard Brendan Parsons, 7th Earl of Rosse (often known simply as Brendan Rosse; born 21 October 1936), is an Anglo-Irish  peer. He is also 10th Baronet Parsons, of Birr Castle.
